The paper discusses the impact of DDoS attacks on cloud resources and proposes defense mechanisms against them. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper also discusses the differences in defense mechanisms between traditional networks and cloud computing, which could fall under distributed systems (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), and systems and control (cs.SY).
